# Day 1155

![](https://miro.medium.com/1*THybPhE3yb_u5LMh2cyavA.png)

Had the chance to visit my buddy Keenan today and check out the Manhattan views from his rooftop in Jersey City. Absolutely stunning.

I always say I'm happy I don't live in NEW YORK CITY, but man is nyc so fun to visit. It's busy. Crowded. Kind of dirty. But it's also one of the coolest places to be.

The energy, the vibe, the fact you can do something 24/7/365 is quite special. Man it's a treat to visit.

Grateful to have friends and family in the area. Also grateful to live in Florida.

I do not take any of it for grantedðŸ’¯

5/20/25

Conor Jay Chepenik
